    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E92 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance featuring the S65 4.0L V8 and its distinctive 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque distribution. The vehicle retains its original factory finish with zero imperfections, and the cabin remains in showroom state, free of typical leather fatigue. Comprehensive service records confirm that critical preventative measures\u2014specifically rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator upgrades\u2014have been completed. With its carbon fiber roof and taut, communicative chassis, this is a definitive example of the final high-revving M-division era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
