    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or inclement weather. The exterior finish is flawless, protected by a full-front paint protection film (PPF) and a professional-grade ceramic coating that yields a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks or stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather retains its original matte finish and factory scent, with zero wear on the seat bolsters, steering wheel, or switchgear. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive binder containing every service record since new, all performed by master technicians using only genuine OEM parts. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full synthetic oil service, brake fluid flush, and a fresh set of high-performance tires with less than 500 miles on them. No accidents, no modifications, and a strictly smoke-free/pet-free history. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
